metadata.name: Meet me at Blue Hour.
metadata.description:
The world turns quiet as it envelops in a shade of blue.  It’s a fleeting moment where the world begins to say goodnight.  Blue hour is gentle and you can start to feel like you are dreaming while you are awake before the day officially turns into night.  Memories of the day begin to integrate accompanied by the unknown of the next.  
I’ll see you at blue hour.


Edition - 1/1 Photography NFT  
Artist - Sara Boychuk

About Sara B - Sara Boychuk is a photographer nestled close to the Canadian Rockies. She is known for her icey cold and blue landscapes and often referred to as the "ice queen".  She can also be seen photographing adventurous portraits or sharing her adventures on youtube.
